topic.title: What kind of resources are present in zeronet?
topic.body:
Hi guys, i would like to know what kind of resources i can find on zeronet? is it like deepweb? Government secrets, ufo, other? Can you help me to know if it's possible to find things that there isn't on "normal web"? Thank you.

Problema.

1585090638_1nADL2gz5MoAsEjnoARpP4hPTVfBk.body:
> [nekololi](#comment_445_1FzZsDQdh8wk71bDLxURPzmAt2FXehoNAB): zeronet has a pretty solid resource of lolis and alternative political beliefs. i don't think there is any "content" you can find on zeronet that you cannot find on the regular world wide web.

ok, so zeronet is "only" one different way to see the web?
